title: Requires utility companies to employ only competent workers skilled in excavation or construction projects when working on a public thoroughfare
summary: Requires utility companies to employ only competent workers skilled in excavation or construction projects when working on a public thoroughfare of the state, county or municipality.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the labor law, in relation to requiring utility companies to employ only competent workers skilled in the work of excavation or construction projects when working on a public thoroughfare of the state, county or municipality
